Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:05.66,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,等等 納多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:07.31,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要跟來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:08.87,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你真煩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.36,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我負責的區域就在莉可你的正上方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:13.58,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,說起來確實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:21.55,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,那回去時要幫我搬運遺物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:23.00,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,憑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.06,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,因為今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:29.14,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我要當赤笛中審核量最高的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:30.53,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:34.69,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,這片區域大部分已經被搜查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:37.24,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,已經沒什麼稀罕物了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.88,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,那就以多取勝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:41.91,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,那樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:45.92,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,拿之前那東西充數怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:47.53,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你之前偷偷藏起來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:49.26,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,星之羅盤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.76,0:00:50.81,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,那個不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:54.73,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,那個是指引我們發現深淵真相的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.27,0:00:57.94,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,但是如果私藏的事被發現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:00.41,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,這次就不只是被裸吊起來這麼簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:03.64,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,少女的心理陰影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:05.37,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,總之小心點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:08.86,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,啊 大吊籃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.41,0:01:12.72,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,納多 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:14.56,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,那個是600公尺組的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.61,0:01:15.81,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:20.44,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,啊 已經看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:23.45,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,真好 我也想坐坐看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:26.66,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,吶 今天是不是有點太安靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.36,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,是不是沒有錘嘴鳥的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:31.60,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,完全聽不到叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:33.05,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:35.20,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,隨便了 聽不見也好辦事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:38.15,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,那些傢伙會把發光的東西帶回巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:40.51,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:42.41,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你怎麼走我前面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:43.95,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我才是領頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:45.47,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.96,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,今天要挖個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:02:00.83,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,讓隊長也無話可說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:05.82,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.28,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,要拿審核第一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:14.75,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:18.23,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:23.70,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,三個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:26.46,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,四個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:28.24,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,五個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:35.77,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,在祈禱的遺骨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.97,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,很久沒看到了 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:41.27,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,抱歉打擾你長眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:45.14,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我還是挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:50.73,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,照這樣升到600公尺組也是遲早的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:53.80,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.24,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,喂 納多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:58.05,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,快來幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:00.89,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,真沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:02.61,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,他人去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:05.68,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,納多那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:14.43,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,血蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.94,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,為什麼在這麼淺的地方會遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:22.37,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,納多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.71,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不好 那是血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:27.59,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:32.06,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,納多要…被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:41.17,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.12,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,手臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:55.67,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,沒斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:57.37,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,納多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.99,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,誰來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.59,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.57,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,化石之樹竟然融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:15.48,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我是被誰給救了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:24.93,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.76,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.23,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不是吧 沒有呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.41,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,趕緊人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.29,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,這個觸感是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.96,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,他不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.04,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,機…機器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:15.70,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:17.70,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,還是第一次見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:19.59,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,還有些溫熱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.83,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,之前還在動的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.51,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,但是這孩子是從哪裡來的
