Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.32,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.28,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,好 納多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.24,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,還差一點就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.28,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.98,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,等一下才是最要命的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.16,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.96,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,原來是西吉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.93,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,嚇我一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:42.59,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,他是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:43.81,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:46.64,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,姑且叫他機器君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:47.53,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:49.47,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.19,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,莉可又想私藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.35,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,只是想幫他躲起來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.58,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,隨便你怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:59.68,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,果然在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.84,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,院長 我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.20,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,趕緊進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:07.69,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,怎麼過她那關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.51,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,或許我有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:20.45,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,幾維
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:22.96,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.97,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,那樣能說明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.76,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,希望可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.53,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,書 書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:51.29,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,說幾次你才明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:54.02,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不要在陽台看書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:56.72,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,下次再這樣就把書沒收
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.10,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,昨天辛苦大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:16.78,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,挖掘的數量雖然不太理想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:19.38,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,但大家基本上都是第一次單獨作業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:20.91,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:23.51,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,下週也是同樣的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:26.74,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,在100m的深度繼續作業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:30.34,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,有裝備丟失的向總務申請
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:31.20,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我說完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:35.37,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,院長有話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:39.92,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我要說的只有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:44.20,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,持鈴生要有作為孤兒院學生的自覺性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.58,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,努力賺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:50.15,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不要給你們在別處的親人們丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.74,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,啊 還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:53.81,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,二件了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:54.79,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,二件了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:58.64,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,私藏遺物是嚴令禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.88,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,好像在瞪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:07.00,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,遺物是孤兒院重要的收入來源
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.52,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,要是敢中飽私囊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.12,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,到時候被怎麼懲罰…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:13.60,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,都不要有怨言喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.33,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:18.38,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,下次就不是裸吊起來這麼簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:19.69,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,希望你們能記住這點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:20.94,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我說完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:22.04,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,解散
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:25.17,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,沒有暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:26.55,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:28.21,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:30.00,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你留下來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:33.12,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你是說納多的登山包丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.44,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,是因為被血蛇襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:36.68,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.57,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.86,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,要不是我救了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.58,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,納多那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:42.56,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,現在已經是蛇的便便了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:43.55,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你救了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:44.29,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:48.36,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我用笛子發出嗶-的聲音成為誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.29,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,然後 你又是怎樣得救的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:53.57,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,那時候真是驚險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.08,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,有一道從未見過的光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:11:59.57,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:02.88,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,差點把機器君的事說出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:04.01,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:07.43,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,就算是相對安全的100公尺深度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.14,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,也說不定會出現什麼意外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.92,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,今後可不要放鬆警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:16.65,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:19.41,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.36,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:26.80,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,請把我分配到更深的區域去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:31.29,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我不是說過等你達到最大的審查額再考慮的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:36.85,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,先學會更高效的探窟技巧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:40.78,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我想儘快累積深部探窟的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.80,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,儘快成為白笛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.69,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,然後追趕上母親的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:48.85,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,去母親下潛過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:49.45,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:53.82,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,再說了 就憑現在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:57.07,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,下潛到400m的地方頂多能跑個來回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:13:00.25,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,暫時就給我老老實實幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:11.81,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是遺憾 救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.26,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.45,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,偷聽什麼的太沒品了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:17.04,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,話說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.25,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你房間裡的「那個」準備怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:20.47,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,機器人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.44,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,當然是叫醒他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:24.03,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,那傢伙原來是在睡覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:26.47,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,對 得早點叫醒他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:28.95,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,所以 大家幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:32.33,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,怎樣 怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:33.83,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,好像稍微動了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:35.09,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.04,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.58,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,試著稍微增強一點怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:40.59,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,小孩子的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:42.52,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,{\an8}對了 莉可 把刻度調到2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:45.95,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:49.45,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,再睡一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.51,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.28,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我說西吉 可以按了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.14,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,莉可 那不是20嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.38,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.41,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:16.77,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,看吧看吧 和我說的一樣電流很有效吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:19.01,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,{\an8}剛才說餵他吃燃煤的人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.20,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,吶 吶 機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:24.26,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你記得我嗎 是你救了我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:27.10,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你是怎麼從那麼遠的地方把蛇收拾掉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:29.76,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不過 先告訴我你的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:32.07,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,喂 你一口氣說太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.08,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,都嚇到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:36.78,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,對不起 我的名字叫莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:39.68,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,雖然用提問來回答不太禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:44.73,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,說話了 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:45.92,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我想問幾個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:48.37,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,什麼什麼 什麼都可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.49,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,這裡是…哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:51.37,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.24,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,這是我的房間喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:54.64,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,貝爾切洛孤兒院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:59.46,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你們的工作是 拷問嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:03.28,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,莉可的房間以前是處刑的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.72,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,因為玩笑開過頭了 所以搬到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:09.50,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,而且 我們的工作是探窟家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:12.28,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,雖然這麼說 也只不過是見習的赤笛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:15.73,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,吶 吶 機器人 你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.39,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,都有什麼功能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.37,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,是誰製造的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:25.42,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,從剛才開始就很在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:29.08,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我 是機器人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:33.88,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,是啊 通電就能動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:35.49,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不怕火燒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.73,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,皮膚也刀槍不入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:42.00,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,啊 你連自己是機器人都不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:44.75,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,因為剛才的電流失憶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:46.72,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,大事不妙了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:49.60,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,孤兒院的電全都停了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:53.16,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,可能是剛才功率輸出過頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:54.92,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,快點藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.03,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,隊長直接來這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:58.99,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,怎麼會暴露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.76,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,是平時的品行問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:01.69,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.88,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不把這個拿掉不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:05.84,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:11.55,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,莉可 巧妙地糊弄過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:12.74,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,真是不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.76,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不能出來喔 明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.58,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不然下場會很慘的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.43,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,喂 莉可 快開門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.73,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,好 馬上…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.78,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你這次又做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:42.12,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,沒幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.67,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,比起這那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:48.02,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,剛才腳撞到了 角度很正
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.92,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,真的痛死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:53.16,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,真的撞得很剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:53.91,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.28,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,這東西是西吉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.37,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,又是些不明所以的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:07.18,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,喂 你有什麼要說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.80,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,對不起 我再也不敢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:14.43,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我明白你探窟不順感到焦慮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.61,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,但就算這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:20.03,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,也沒有讓整個孤兒院停電的道理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.21,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,莉可 你在聽嗎 莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:30.79,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,在你解釋清楚這慘狀之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:35.30,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,先給我打掃孤兒院和寫檢討書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.87,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:44.69,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:46.44,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,如果被那傢伙抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:47.97,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,下場會很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.04,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.32,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,手腕竟然能夠伸長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:18:00.48,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,伸縮的金屬手腕和這個頭盔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.17,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,更加覺得可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.12,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我…到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.53,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,機器人也需要肚臍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:20.23,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,這…這個也需要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:29.00,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我趁著西吉他們被抓住的間隙溜出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.42,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.31,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,在鏡子前打扮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:34.40,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:35.50,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:37.94,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:38.96,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:39.61,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,跑哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.50,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 得快點逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:44.76,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,抓緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:45.88,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,趕緊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:01.73,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,好厲害 這手真方便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:05.35,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.85,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,莉可 跑哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.91,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,看來他暫時消不了氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.41,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,對了 我有東西想要給雷格看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:14.37,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,雷格?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:17.68,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你的名字 沒名字的話很不方面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.58,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,雷格 這名字怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:22.94,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我倒不介意 順便問一下怎麼來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.28,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,之前養的小狗的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:26.77,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:30.47,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,雷格 快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.05,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:49.04,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,馬上就來了 雷格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:13.90,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,雷格 這就是我們居住的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:16.59,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,巨穴之城奧斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.62,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到奧斯 雷格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:31.81,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,這個巨穴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:36.20,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,雷格 你連阿比斯 都忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:37.52,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.32,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,這個巨穴叫做阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:42.41,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,你就是從阿比斯裡面被找到的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:44.21,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:46.75,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我在想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.31,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,雷格會不會是從阿比斯的底部來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:52.07,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:54.88,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次看見你這樣的機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:56.48,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,一定是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:59.83,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,誰都沒有去過的…阿比斯的底部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:02.79,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:11.10,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,約1900年前 南海貝歐魯斯卡的孤島上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.61,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,發現了一個巨大的豎型巨穴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:19.97,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,直徑約1000m  其深度至今無人知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:24.25,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,它那不可思議的姿態深深吸引著人們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:28.23,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,珍貴而又危險的原始生物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:31.03,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,和超出認知的不可思議的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:34.41,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,誘惑著想要一夜暴富的冒險者們蜂擁而至
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:38.73,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,不知何時 這裡已經建立起了巨大的小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:42.09,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,經過長年累月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:45.76,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,以未知的浪漫和眾多的傳說為餌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:48.40,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,將不計其數的人們吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:51.00,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,世界上唯一的最後的深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:54.99,Made in Abyss,,0,0,0,,其名為「阿比斯」
